{"tid":949462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民航處食屎啦  一取消規管燃油附加費 班仆街航空公司就加快減慢","createTime":"2018-12-20T21:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T06:43:22.000Z","uid":136994,"like":73,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"86e1619b90c28bebb5857ef8d8eeba25c9344eca","tid":949462,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T21:49:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪民航處<br />\n以前燃油附加費個規管機制明明運作得好地地<br />\n都真係會根據油價升跌調整<br />\n點解冇端端要取消個規管<br />\n畀班商家亂嚟？<br />\n由其係冚家鏟因航<br />\n一取消規管就急不及待收燃油附加費<br />\n而家油價跌到四十幾美金一桶啦<br />\n因航仲收緊長途六百幾蚊一程吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母政府應管嘅就唔管<br />\n唔撚應該管就管<br />\n食屎啦"},{"pid":"c62c2302adba49b3d9c6038de7ef315326d3acdb","tid":949462,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T22:19:26.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味 減就慢 加就快到痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bb43fea1181309a9d63c3485473f8cbe1a6a9c","tid":949462,"uid":51701,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T22:22:34.000Z","msg":"民航處<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民用航空公司聯合辦事處"},{"pid":"4e6dad1c515c58dacd530978b474dfbad7c0b248","tid":949462,"uid":20058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T22:30:43.000Z","msg":"自由市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c98ca844d7aa1c2b78d46efb1d0155120fa7d03","tid":949462,"uid":136994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T00:35:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱呢兩個月嘅油價跌幅<br />\n已經令到一年嘅升幅無曬不單止就有突<br />\n燃油附加費呢？<br />\n垃圾民航處食屎啦"},{"pid":"98903fadf84d9dee4875f51b1ed90295bf22939b","tid":949462,"uid":6604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T00:38:10.000Z","msg":"航空公司想吸客咪減附加費囉<br />\n但係我淨係見到一話放寬<br />\n就個個一齊加<br />\n冇話邊個係evil<br />\n邊個係lesser evil<br />\n大家都想搵錢"},{"pid":"f9d0e8a909e94c15fee0b